# Free Google reviews widget (no credit card required)
#
# --- Trustindex (recommended) ---
# 1. Sign up free at https://www.trustindex.io/
# 2. Connect "Venkateswara LED Display" on Google Maps
# 3. Widget configurator → Save and get code → copy the loader.js URL
# 4. Paste below, copy this file to .env, restart: npm run dev
#
VITE_TRUSTINDEX_LOADER_URL=https://cdn.trustindex.io/loader.js?YOUR_WIDGET_ID
VITE_TRUSTINDEX_WIDGET_ID=YOUR_WIDGET_ID
#
# --- Elfsight (alternative) ---
# VITE_REVIEWS_WIDGET_PROVIDER=elfsight
# VITE_ELFSIGHT_APP_ID=your-elfsight-app-id
